com.googlecode.mrsqg.analysis
Class Pair

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.mrsqg.analysis.Pair

public class Pair
extends java.lang.Object

A class to hold all sentence/question pairs, including the intermediate results, such as MRS representations. Generally, a MrsTransformer uses it to store s/q pairs generated from original sentences, and a Fallback uses it to store s/q pairs by re-generation from transformed sentences.

Author:
Xuchen Yao

public java.lang.String getGenOriCand()

Returns:
a sentence string, or null if not found
